1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:07,500
Mi lómë cemessë,
In the silence of the earth,

2
00:00:07,500 --> 00:00:15,000
yassë súrë yesta,
where the wind begins to call,

3
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:22,500
síressë, ëarissë,
by the river, by the sea,

4
00:00:22,500 --> 00:00:30,000
nórë nu lómë esta
there’s a hidden world for all

5
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:35,000
Mi taurë lómëa nu,
Through the forest, dark and deep,

6
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:40,000
oronti or i alta,
past the mountains standing high,

7
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:45,000
síressë yassë lumbor caita,
by the lake where shadows sleep,

8
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:50,000
menel nu pella
underneath the open sky

9
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:55,000
Aiwi lírir mi súrë,
Trees are whispering in the air,

10
00:00:55,000 --> 00:01:00,000
lótë liltë calaressë,
Flowers dancing in the light,

11
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:05,000
sarnë caita nárë,
Rocks are resting everywhere,

12
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:10,000
tulir lindalë lómessë
Guiding travelers through the night

13
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:15,000
Nén sirya ar uru calë,
Water flows and fire burns,

14
00:01:15,000 --> 00:01:20,000
cemë tulca nu talma,
Earth is strong beneath our feet,

15
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:25,000
súrë orta ar váta,
Wind will rise and slowly turn,

16
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:30,000
vilya ar menel ar ilya
Air and sky and all we meet

17
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:35,000
Olvar orta ar rávar norta,
Plants will grow and animals run,

18
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:40,000
fanyar hosta mi luinë,
Clouds will gather in the blue,

19
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:45,000
lossë lanta ar anar túra,
Rain will fall, then comes the sun,

20
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:50,000
caitalë ilyë lírë
Painting life in every hue

21
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:52,500
Raumo tula, hlarë rómë,
Storm is coming, hear the sound,

22
00:01:52,500 --> 00:01:55,000
calma rista menel,
Lightning cuts across the sky,

23
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:57,500
lossë ar aiwë lanta cemen,
Snow and hail fall to the ground,

24
00:01:57,500 --> 00:02:00,000
valiëa túrë orta
Nature’s power rising high

25
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:05,000
Ar lómë enta tula,
Then the silence comes again,

26
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:10,000
isil or ar eleni cala,
Moon above and stars so bright,

27
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:15,000
mi i nórë varya ar auta,
In this world of loss and gain,

28
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:20,000
nárë lindë aurë ar lómë
Nature sings… through day and night

